             </blockquote>
           <p><strong>Q12. In the attendance page of the OASIS, I don't see any indication that my ward was present or not.      </strong></p>
           <blockquote>
             <p>A12. There is a legend placed in the attendance page indicating whether your ward was present or not.                        </blockquote>
